Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.41,0:22:38.70,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}上目づかいなり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.41,0:22:38.70,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}是暧昧的眼神
