Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.90,0:22:56.49,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}这份距离也
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.61,0:22:59.85,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}いけてるんです
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.61,0:22:59.85,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}感觉还不错
