Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.45,0:23:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前就这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.60,0:23:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.80,0:23:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前从学校放学回来的时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.50,0:23:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.09,0:23:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美月小姐 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.78,0:24:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把围绕在大小姐旁边的杂草都割啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.22,0:24:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是爱担心
